            <description><![CDATA[
                <h2>Clippy 2.0 — The Ember Redesign 🧡</h2>
                <p>Every screen has been rebuilt in a warm, branded design language we call <strong>Ember</strong>.</p>
                <h3>Highlights</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Brand-new look — amber accent, rounded typography, card-based history</li>
                    <li>Context-aware Inspector panel across the app</li>
                    <li>Screenshot editor reimagined with Studio Bar + Inspector</li>
                    <li>Windows-style Dock Preview animations</li>
                    <li>Privacy & Permissions panel with one-click reset</li>
                </ul>
                <p><a href="https://github.com/yarasaa/Clippy/releases/tag/v2.0.0">Full release notes</a></p>
